                <li>Native Google Docs, WordPress, and Word integrations</li>
                <li>Used by Condé Nast, Shopify, and HubSpot</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h5>Trade-offs</h5>
              <ul class="no-list">
                <li>No AI writer included</li>
                <li>No free trial — pay before testing</li>
                <li>Business plan jumps to $399/mo</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="tool-card-foot">
            <div class="tool-best-for"><strong>Best for:</strong> Large editorial teams that prioritize simplicity and collaboration.</div>
            <a href="https://clearscope.io" class="tool-cta-btn" rel="nofollow">Visit site →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- #6 Scalenut -->
        <div class="tool-card">
          <div class="tool-card-head">
            <div class="tool-rank">06</div>
            <div class="tool-card-info">
              <div class="tool-card-name">Scalenut</div>
              <div class="tool-card-tag">Best all-in-one on a budget</div>
            </div>
            <div class="tool-card-price">
              <div class="price">$30<span style="font-size: 14px; color: var(--text-3);">/mo</span></div>
              <div class="per">Starter annual</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="tool-card-body">
            <div>
              <h5>What it does better</h5>
              <ul class="yes-list">
                <li>80% cheaper than Rankability on annual billing</li>
                <li>Bundles AI writing, optimization, and WP publishing</li>
